<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    </head>
    <body>
        <p>Hello <%= @attendee.first_name %> <%= @attendee.last_name %>,</p>

        <p>Thank you for registering for the FEP Finance and Audit Meeting in Austin, TX.</p>

        <p>You will first need to download the iPhone/iPad app or the Android app. Alternatively, you can login to the web version at <a href='https://fep-fa.eventkaddy.net'>https://fep-fa.eventkaddy.net</a></p>

        <p>Once you have downloaded the app on your device, open the app, and then choose FEP Finance and Audit Meeting from the event listing.</p>

        <p>Your login is the email you used to register: <%= @email %></p>

        <p>Your unique password is: <%= @password %></p>

        <p>To download the iPhone/iPad app, please follow this link:</p>
        <p><a href='https://itunes.apple.com/ca/app/fep-events/id1465172847?mt=8'>https://itunes.apple.com/ca/app/fep-events/id1465172847?mt=8</a></p>

        <p>To download the Android app, please follow this link:</p>
        <p><a href='https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bcbsa.fep'>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bcbsa.fep</a></p>

        <p>You can also search for the app in the app stores by app name: FEP Events.</p>

        <p>If you are logged into the FEP National Conference, please go to Settings and select Change Event and then choose FEP Finance and Audit Meeting from the event listing.</p>

        <p>Should you need assistance to download the new app, please visit the Mobile App Support desk at the conference. Support will be onsite beginning Sunday, August 25 during registration hours. You can also email for support help by contacting <a href='mailto:techsupport@eventkaddy.com'>techsupport@eventkaddy.com</a>.</p>
  </body>
</html>
